how to draw by overlaying step-by-step guides on your piece of paper.\nLearn fundamental concepts such as:\n- Shape & Form\n- Perspective\n- Texture\n- Anatomy\n- & More!\n\n{870538865095490}\nCreate your own still-life composition with Free-draw mode. Drag and drop 3d and 2d models onto a stage that get projected onto your paper.\n", "short_description": "Pencil! - Learn how to draw with real paper and pencil! \n\nUsing mixed-reality, overlay step-by-step guides to trace and learn the fundamentals of drawing. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://pencil-xr.com/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "4th Wall Breakers", "support_website_url": "https://www.pencilxr.com/discord", "website_url": "https://www.pencilxr.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}, {"id": "393222478507326"}, {"id": "323450648956687"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8358998234135234"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1117205959385750"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1117205959385750"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1726231500, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1117205959385750"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8494198877281835", "version": "0.2.11"}, "id": "33264331